      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELLE'S MOON (1) boasts a strong record this course with three wins and four minors from eight tries. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (29.89) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 1.3 lengths fourth. Expected to be in the finish. ESCAPADES (2) was checked in the run and safely held when fourth (30.13) in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Can do much better this time. PRINCESS ADA (5) is in sizzling form lately, rocketing around this track in 29.61 to score two back then following on with a 29.75 win over 520m at this track. Flying lately and can measure up again. ZIPPING SMEE (6) will have admirers after surprising many with a placing last time out.",
